{"tid":846289,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【打工皇帝】蘋果派獎勵股份 每名高層3,000萬美元","createTime":"2018-10-03T10:15:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-03T11:01:03.000Z","uid":28765,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0aed5d74a6b6ed3928b8843e0fe46e64ecd6422d","tid":846289,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T10:15:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181003/large/1538552022_344b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181003%2Flarge%2F1538552022_344b.png&h=01d4923d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n蘋果高級副總裁Katherine Adams(互聯網)<br />\n蘋果公司的最高級別高層，上周獲頒佈股權獎勵計劃，每人可獲得超過3,000萬美元的股份，包括負責全球安全事務和法律事務的高級副總裁Katherine Adams、負責蘋果零售店業務的Angela Ahrendts、CFO Luca Maestri、COO Jeff Williams。<br />\n上述四人，每人將獲得約8.86萬股受限制蘋果股份，於2023年4月或以前派發，一半須因應公司股東回報而定。若公司的指標能達成，加上該名高層仍維持相對現有職級，便可獲得約13.29萬股蘋果股份，相當於3,050萬美元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20181003/58751716\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181003%2F58751716&d=%2BX40yYmwoEG9YEvn5HZpUe9M5Ue6CDmcYDZznX2R1Ws%3D&h=f228cc18\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181003%2F58751716&h=84e2631a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20181003/58751716</a>"},{"pid":"1bc1b5ee3d64bd4f8c7d9315ce19bbd2d8f2efcf","tid":846289,"uid":46943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T10:54:52.000Z","msg":"一班管理層夾計分利潤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4faf61745508479704587ee0af8e181b88b938a","tid":846289,"uid":13663,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T10:59:15.000Z","msg":"Amazon<br />\nApple<br />\n美國大企業都開始加人工 派錢<br />\n經濟好到仆街 又同員工分享成果<br />\n消費升級 GDP上升<br />\n好似貿易戰真係贏硬咁<img s